---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Hesaa">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[80ch] px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-8">About</h1>
    <div class="text-base text-primary leading-[1.7] space-y-6">
      <p>
        I'm Hesaa, a Software Engineer based in Bogor, Indonesia. I have over 5 years of experience architecting high-performance, secure, and scalable backend systems.
      </p>
      <p>
        I specialize in TypeScript (Node.js) and PHP (Laravel). My work centers around building robust financial and marketplace transaction platforms — including PPOB, POS, and escrow systems. I care deeply about database design, Redis caching, API security, and comprehensive error monitoring.
      </p>
      <p>
        Most recently, I was a Back-End Developer at PT. Badr Interactive, where I developed features for Indonesia's national healthcare system (SMILE). Before that, I spent nearly 5 years building the back-end architecture for AWAN, a high-volume multi-biller PPOB and POS platform.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary pt-4">What I Work With</h2>
      <p>
        Node.js (TypeScript, Express, Hono) · PHP (Laravel, CodeIgniter) · Python (FastAPI) · PostgreSQL · MySQL · Redis · RESTful APIs · Docker · CI/CD
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary pt-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Reach me at <a href="mailto:hesa7511@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:text-interactive transition-colors underline underline-offset-2 decoration-border">hesa7511@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
